sentences.quote:
	exttt{BundleRiemannAux.lean} opens the Bonn-API bundle scope with a bare-function bundle Riemann curvature $R(X, Y)Z = 
abla_{X}
abla_{Y}Z - 
abla_{Y}
abla_{X}Z - 
abla_{[X,Y]}Z$ consuming 	exttt{IsCovariantDerivativeOn} and 	exttt{VectorField.mlieBracket}, with the wave-headlines $R(X, X)Z = 0$ and $R(X, Y)Z = -R(Y, X)Z$, plus a commuting-vector-fields specialisation and zero-degeneracies for the section and the X-slot on Bonn's 	exttt{IsCovariantDerivativeOn.zero};

